project:
Virgil Security provides an SDK which allows you to communicate with Virgil Brainkey Service and implement Brainkey protocol in order to generate user's Brainkey. Brainkey is a user's Private Key that is generated from a user's password. Brainkey can be easily restored and is resistant to online and offline attacks.
Enable multi-threading safety for Brainkey SDK.
